}}</ref>后毕业于[[普林斯顿大学|普林斯顿大学]]和[[斯坦福大学|斯坦福大学]]。<ref name="projectpengyou_chang">{{cite web |URL=https://projectpengyou.org/fateful-ties-a-conversation-with-author-gordon-chang/ |title=Fateful Ties: A Conversation with Professor Gordon H. Chang |publisher=projectpengyou.org |date=July 12, 2015 |accessdate=August 13, 2019 |archive-date=2019-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190814040446/https://projectpengyou.org/fateful-ties-a-conversation-with-author-gordon-chang/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="stanford_chang2019">{{cite web |URL=https://news.stanford.edu/2019/03/21/gordon-h-chang-become-senior-associate-vice-provost-undergraduate-education/ |title=Gordon H. Chang to become senior associate vice provost for undergraduate education |publisher=news.stanford.edu |first=Eric |last=Van Danen |date=March 21, 1999 |accessdate=August 13, 2019 |archive-date=2019-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191019132217/https://news.stanford.edu/2019/03/21/gordon-h-chang-become-senior-associate-vice-provost-undergraduate-education/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2015年加入[[百人会|百人会]]。<ref>{{cite web |URL=https://www.committee100.org/announcements/dr-gordon-h-chang-stanford-university-east-asia-center-director-becomes-a-committee-of-100-member/ |title=Dr. Gordon H. Chang, Stanford University East Asia Center Director, Becomes a Committee of 100 Member |publisher=committee100.org |date=2015 |accessdate=August 13, 2019 |archive-date=2019-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190814035035/https://www.committee100.org/announcements/dr-gordon-h-chang-stanford-university-east-asia-center-director-becomes-a-committee-of-100-member/ }}</ref>

==著作==
张少书教授著有： 
*''Friends and Enemies: The United States, China and the Soviet Union, 1948-1972'' (1990) ISBN 0804715653, 梅寅生 译：《敌乎？友乎？—美国分化中苏联盟内幕》，台湾金禾出版社1992年版 ISBN 9578573014
*  Morning ''Glory, Evening Shadow: Yamato Ichihashi and His Wartime Writing, 1942-1945'' (1997), 
*''Asian Americans and Politics: An Exploration'' (2001), and 
*''Chinese American Voices: From the Gold Rush to the Present'' (2006).

==荣誉==
1999年获得古根海姆学者奖。

